{"word":"ἐνεχυράζω","slug":"ἐνεχυράζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνεχυράζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>άσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἐνέχῠρον</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to take a pledge from</i> one, <el>τινός</el> Lex <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to take in pledge</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to have one's</i> goods <i>seized for debt</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to have security given one, take it for oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}